articles.author: Dave Itzkoff
articles.title: ‘S.N.L.’ Presents Kellyanne Conway’s ‘Marriage Story,’ Plus Baby Yoda
articles.description: It was a Christmas miracle: “Saturday Night Live” opened the show with a sketch that wasn’t dependent on celebrity cameos.
articles.content:
The dinner guests around Strongs table wondered who could possibly vote for Trump now, while at Bennetts table they asked how anyone couldnt vote for him. To his family, Thompson asked, Who do you think is going to get voted off The Masked Singer next week?
